  "keyFeatures": [
    "100% CommonMark 0.31.2 compliant parser and renderer",
    "Full GitHub Flavored Markdown (GFM) support with strikethrough, tables, task lists, and autolinks",
    "AST-based parsing with typed arena for safe memory management",
    "Multiple output formats: HTML, CommonMark, and XML",
    "Extensive extension system including footnotes, superscript, description lists, math, and wikilinks",
    "CLI tool with syntax highlighting and multiple output formats",
    "Plugin architecture for custom syntax highlighting and formatters",
    "Safe-by-default with optional unsafe HTML rendering",
    "Used by crates.io, docs.rs, GitLab, Deno, and Reddit"
  ],
